      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "Last time, I got #p103# some mushroom caps and boar's teeth to convince her dad to let her travel. That didn't work. Now she has a new dream: she wants to be an alchemist! A bit fickle, but whatever. Now, she needs materials... I can guess where this is going. She wants me to collect #b1 #t2022000#, 25 #t4000036#, and 25 #t4000039##k by defeating several monsters so she can make some #t2000004#s."
