  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hey! You helped me the other day! You know, even after I showed my dad the items you got me, he still wouldn't let me travel... Hmph. He said he knew I didn't get them myself."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I gave up on that dream shortly afterwards. Ah well. Anyway, I want to ask you for another favor... Do you have time?"
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirName": "2",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I have a new dream. Being a traveler would be too tough for a pretty girl like me, hehe, so my new life ambition is to become a great alchemist! Oh, by the way! Do you know what an alchemist does? Even if you do, I’ll give you a simple explanation again so it’s easy to understand."
      },
      "3": {
        "_dirName": "3",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "An alchemist is someone who can freely handle various objects that exist in this world, and with special techniques, transform them into something entirely new. In other words, it’s a profession that can craft items imbued with mysterious powers from different materials."
      },
      "4": {
        "_dirName": "4",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "So here’s the thing… to make different items, I’ll need materials. If you’re not too busy, could you gather the ones I tell you about? In return, I’ll make sure you get whatever item is created. I can’t promise exactly what it’ll turn out to be… but what do you think?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Awesome! Let's see... I'm going to need #b1 #t2022000##k, #b25 #t4000036##k, and #b25 #t4000039##k. Also, please take care of #r50 #o40#s and 50 #o43#s#k. If all goes well, I can make #t2000004#s! "
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Well, now. If you don't have time to listen to a poor girl's plea... Fine, just let me know if you change your mind."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Yippee! You got #b1 #t2022000##k, #b25 #t4000036##k, and #b25 #t4000039##k! Now, my turn. I just gotta mix these babies together and..."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Voila! You know, this is my first time actually doing alchemy. Am I good or what? Here you go. Please take it as a gift."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Wow. I've got a talent for this. I made 10 #r#t2000004#s#k during my very first experiment. You did your part to help, of course! Thank you."
        }
      },
